Education information: Beijing compressed 2016 junior high school admissions special talent student ratio - Xinhua 21, 22 two, Beijing junior high school admissions special talent student examination work by the unified organization and implementation of each district education committee. This year, all districts in Beijing have compressed the proportion of special students enrolled in the special students, special students competition is more intense. In Dongcheng District, for example, this year, the district's elementary school to junior high school special students enrollment ratio overall does not exceed 5% of the district's enrollment plan, the number of planned enrollment of 380 people, to school ratio does not exceed 10% of the school's enrollment plan. All students with special talents in sports, arts, science and technology and online registration are eligible to participate in the special student enrollment examination. In order to facilitate students to participate in the examination nearby, Dongcheng District continued last year's examination arrangement, setting up 1~2 examination sites in each school district, a total of 13 examination sites. The test sites are divided by test area, divided into time slots by hour, the test day students will enter the test site in time slots in different test areas for the test, May 23, the district education admissions test center online list of students who passed the test, students can check the test results online.
